<tr>
<td style="background-color: #61af3f;" width="634">
<p style="color: #ffffff; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 32px; line-height: 34px; text-align: center; font-weight: bold; margin: 25px 15px 25px 15px;">HURRY! Refer your friends today:<br /><a style="color: #ffffff; text-decoration: none;" href="http://www.directenergysolar.com/refer">directenergysolar.com/refer</a></p>
</td>
