<div class="mktEditable" id="disclaimerCopyTerms" ><p style="color: #666666; font-size: 11px; font-weight: normal; line-height: 16px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-top: 0px;"><span class="appleLinksGray"><sup>1</sup>You must be a Direct Energy Solar customer to participate in the Direct Energy Solar Referral Program. For each referral who signs a contract with Direct Energy Solar between November 25, 2015&ndash;February 29, 2016, you will receive $750. This referral offer is not valid within special community pricing programs or in combination with any other offer&mdash;if your referral receives special community pricing on their solar contract, you will receive $200. Individuals may not refer themselves. Referrals must have no prior contact with Direct Energy Solar to be considered a customer referral. Payment in the form of a check is sent within 60 days of the sale.</span></p>
<p style="color: #666666; font-size: 11px; font-weight: normal; line-height: 16px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-top: 0px;"><span class="appleLinksGray"><sup>2</sup>Should project fail to qualify for the program due to unforeseen circumstances, your referral will have the option to cancel their contract with us.</span></p>
<p style="color: #666666; font-size: 11px; font-weight: normal; line-height: 16px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-top: 0px;"><span class="appleLinksGray">Offers and financing are available to customers who qualify, vary by location, and are not available in all areas. We customize our solar power system specifically for your home, therefore, pricing, savings, utility bill, solar bill amounts and actual returns vary based on different factors including but not limited to your location, system size, available solar incentives and local utility rates. See terms and conditions for more details.</span></p>
